title: What's Worth Streaming: As subscription prices rise, here’s what’s worth streaming in November 2022: ‘The Crown,’ ‘Willow,’ ‘Mythic Quest’ and more
description: The addition of cheaper, ad-supported tiers on Netflix -- and soon Disney+ -- may ease the price pain; meanwhile, a new season of 'The Crown' and a 'Willow' sequel highlight November's new releases.
